{"snippets":[{"id":"Snippet_5F5FCE1205A1BEA0_1600114216982_0","name":"SampleSqlSnippets","snippet":"-- How many files did the user preview? 
SELECT * FROM LM_PREVIEW_TABLE  

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- How many data tables are loaded after preview?
SELECT LT.TABLE_NAME, LT.LOAD_ID, DT.FILE_PATH FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES as LT, (SELECT FILE_PATH, LOAD_ID FROM LM_PREVIEW_TABLE ) AS DT WHERE LT.LOAD_ID == DT.LOAD_ID AND LT.TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%load%'


--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- How many files are only previewed and not loaded as tables?          
SELECT * FROM LM_PREVIEW_TABLE LP LEFT JOIN (SELECT LT.LOAD_ID FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES LT WHERE LT.TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%load%') DT ON LP.LOAD_ID == DT.LOAD_ID WHERE DT.LOAD_ID IS NULL

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- How many types of files are loaded?
SELECT COUNT(FILE_TYPE), FILE_TYPE FROM LM_FILE_TABLE GROUP BY FILE_TYPE

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- Average time taken for parsing files and loading tables?
SELECT AVG(TABLE_EXECUTION_TIME) FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- Min and Max time for parsing files and loading tables
SELECT MIN(ttl_time) as min_execution_time, MAX(ttl_time) as max_execution_time FROM (select sum(TABLE_EXECUTION_TIME) as ttl_time, LOAD_ID from LM_LOADED_TABLES GROUP BY LOAD_ID)

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

-- Histogram of execution times
select sum(TABLE_EXECUTION_TIME) as ttl_time, LOAD_ID from LM_LOADED_TABLES GROUP BY LOAD_ID

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

--What are the tables created?
SELECT TABLE_NAME FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

--What are Min and Max rows of the table?      
SELECT MIN(TABLE_ROW_COUNT), MAX(TABLE_ROW_COUNT) FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES WHERE TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%load'

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

--Table to Number of Files relation
SELECT LT.TABLE_NAME, DT.FILE_COUNT FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES as LT, (SELECT COUNT(FILE_PATH) as FILE_COUNT, LOAD_ID FROM LM_FILE_TABLE GROUP BY LOAD_ID) as DT WHERE DT.LOAD_ID == LT.LOAD_ID AND TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%load' ORDER BY DT.FILE_COUNT DESC

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

--How many tables of compliments with row_count > 0?
SELECT TABLE_NAME, TABLE_ROW_COUNT FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES WHERE TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%comp' AND TABLE_ROW_COUNT > 0

--------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

--Min and Max of tables of compliments?
SELECT MIN(TABLE_ROW_COUNT), MAX(TABLE_ROW_COUNT) FROM LM_LOADED_TABLES WHERE TABLE_TYPE LIKE '%comp' AND TABLE_ROW_COUNT > 0","app":null}]}
